      "text": "Server: server.py (MCP stdio)\nBackend: ChromaDB PersistentClient\nStorage: ~/.claude/chromadb/ (SQLite)\nEmbeddings: all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (local)\nCollections: entities | relations\nSearch: semantic (cosine similarity)\nShared: Windows + WSL same DB",
