    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "flow_summary_text",
      "x": 587,
      "y": 1487,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "1. Phase 0a (Intake): orchestrator -> search_nodes -> ChromaDB -> results -> 00-knowledge-context.md -> agents read\n2. Phase 6 (KG Save): orchestrator -> create_entities (max 3, dedup) -> ChromaDB (MANDATORY post-pipeline)\n3. Phase 4 (Delivery): delivery agent -> CLAUDE.md (4 sections) + docs/knowledge.md\n4. Management: /memory skill -> ChromaDB (search, list, show, stats, prune, consolidate)",
      "originalText": "1. Phase 0a (Intake): orchestrator -> search_nodes -> ChromaDB -> results -> 00-knowledge-context.md -> agents read\n2. Phase 6 (KG Save): orchestrator -> create_entities (max 3, dedup) -> ChromaDB (MANDATORY post-pipeline)\n3. Phase 4 (Delivery): delivery agent -> CLAUDE.md (4 sections) + docs/knowledge.md\n4. Management: /memory skill -> ChromaDB (search, list, show, stats, prune, consolidate)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
